OL,3,CHuman rights groups condemn Rwanda
OL,4,CBill as 'breach of international law'
OL,6,FHuman rights groups have condemned the
OL,7,FGovernment's newly passed Rwanda
OL,8,Fdeportation plan as a "breach of
OL,9,Finternational law".
OL,11,FThe Safety of Rwanda (Asylum and
OL,12,FImmigration) Bill finally passed
OL,13,Fthrough Parliament early on Tuesday
OL,14,Fmorning after numerous disagreements
OL,15,Fled to lengthy "ping-pong" between the
OL,16,Ftwo Houses.
