OL,3,CHuman rights groups condemn Rwanda
OL,4,CBill as 'breach of international law'
OL,6,FThey added the UK was increasingly
OL,7,Fgaining a reputation for "playing fast
OL,8,Fand loose with its international
OL,9,Fobligations" and called for the asylum
OL,10,Fsystem to be rebuilt.
OL,12,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak believes
OL,13,Fsending asylum seekers on the one-way
OL,14,Ftrip to Rwanda could be a strong
OL,15,Fdeterrent to people seeking to cross
OL,16,Fthe English Channel in small boats.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUqD@LO]
