OL,3,CHuman rights groups condemn Rwanda
OL,4,CBill as 'breach of international law'
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the organisations
OL,7,Fsaid: "We all deserve the chance to
OL,8,Flive a safe life, and to seek
OL,9,Fprotection when we need it most. This
OL,10,Fshameful Bill trashes the constitution
OL,11,Fand international law whilst putting
OL,12,Ftorture survivors and other refugees
OL,13,Fat risk of an unsafe future in Rwanda.
OL,15,F"No matter how many times the Prime
OL,16,FMinister says so, we know this is not
OL,17,Fthe will of the people.
OL,26,@oD@GOUwD@AOU
