OL,3,CHuman rights groups condemn Rwanda
OL,4,CBill as 'breach of international law'
OL,6,F"Caring people up and down the UK want
OL,7,Fto see men, women and children who've
OL,8,Ffled war, persecution and torture
OL,9,Fgiven protection and security, so they
OL,10,Fcan recover and rebuild their lives in
OL,11,Fsafety.
OL,13,F"Instead of punishing people who've
OL,14,Falready been through so much, we need
OL,15,Fcompassionate and protection-focused
OL,16,Fpolicies.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
