OL,3,CHuman rights groups condemn Rwanda
OL,4,CBill as 'breach of international law'
OL,6,F"It's time for those in power to stop
OL,7,Fdemonising and scapegoating some of
OL,8,Fthe most vulnerable people in our
OL,9,Fsociety, and to restore the right to
OL,10,Fasylum in the UK and uphold vital
OL,11,Finternational protections."
OL,13,FKolbassia Haoussou, director of
OL,14,Fsurvivor leadership and influencing at
OL,15,FFreedom from Torture, said: "When I
OL,16,Ffled torture in my homeland, the UK
OL,17,Fgranted me sanctuary and a chance to
OL,18,Frebuild my life.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@[O]wD@]OU
