OL,3,CHuman rights groups condemn Rwanda
OL,4,CBill as 'breach of international law'
OL,6,F"But now, people like me could be sped
OL,7,Fonto planes to face an unsafe future
OL,8,Fin Rwanda, and denied the safety and
OL,9,Fsecurity needed for their recovery.
OL,11,F"We know from the work we do in our
OL,12,Ftherapy rooms everyday how terrified
OL,13,Fsurvivors are, and we've seen first-
OL,14,Fhand the awful toll it has taken on
OL,15,Fpeople's mental health.
OL,17,F"We urgently need the UK Government to
OL,18,Fstart treating refugees with decency
OL,19,Fand stop trying to send them thousands
OL,20,Fof miles away."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU|D@OO]
