OL,6,FDenisa Delic, director of advocacy at
OL,7,FInternational Rescue Committee UK,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Rather than outsourcing its
OL,9,Fresponsibilities under international
OL,10,Flaw, we urge the Government to abandon
OL,11,Fthis misguided plan and instead focus
OL,12,Fon delivering a more humane and
OL,13,Forderly immigration system at home.
OL,15,F"This includes scaling up safe routes,
OL,16,Fsuch as resettlement and family
OL,17,Freunion, and upholding the right to
OL,18,Fseek asylum.
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@AOU
