OL,6,F"Sending refugees to Rwanda, or
OL,7,Fanywhere else, will never be an
OL,8,Feffective solution."
OL,10,FMr Sunak acknowledged on Monday that
OL,11,Fthe first planes carrying asylum
OL,12,Fseekers to Rwanda would not take off
OL,13,Funtil July.
OL,15,FAfter that, he said there would be
OL,16,F"multiple flights a month through the
OL,17,Fsummer and beyond".
